\i\fs20 , neutralize poison, remove disease; }{\fs20 1/day\emdash }{\i\fs20 heal }{\fs20 (DC 18)}{\i\fs20 . }{\fs20 Caster level 10th. The save DCs are Charisma-based.
\par }{\b\fs20 Lay on Hands (Su):}{\fs20  As the paladin class feature, except that each day, a leonal can heal an amount of damage equal to its full normal hit points.
\par }{\b\fs20 Protective Aura (Su):}{\fs20  Against attacks made or effects created by evil creatures, this ability provides a +4 deflection bonus to AC 
and a +4 resistance bonus on saving throws to anyone within 20 feet of the leonal. Otherwise, it functions as a }{\i\fs20 magic circle against evil }{\fs20 effect and a }{\i\fs20 lesser globe of invulnerability, }{\fs20 
both with a radius of 20 feet (caster level equals leonal\rquote s HD). (The defensive benefits from the circle are not included in a leonal\rquote s statistics block.)
\par }{\b\fs20 Speak with Animals (Su):}{\fs20  This ability works like }{\i\fs20 speak with animals }{\fs20 (caster level 8th) but is a free action and does not require sound.
\par }{\b\fs20 Skills:}{\fs20  Leonals have a +4 racial bonus on Balance, Hide, and Move Silently checks.}{
