\par The effect cannot be dispelled. Anyone paralyzed by a lich seems dead, though a DC 20 Spot check or a DC 15 Heal check reveals that the victim is still alive..
\par }{\i\fs20 Spells: }{\fs20 A lich can cast any spells it could cast while alive.
